!  Predicted rotator position angle (radians)
!  Pointing origin x & y (millimetres)
!  Telescope focal length (millimetres)
!  Temperature (degrees K)
!  Pressure (mBar)
!  Relative humidity
!  Tropospheric lapse rate
!
